    "ui": "@/components/ui",
    "lib": "@/lib",
    "hooks": "@/hooks"
  },
  "iconLibrary": "lucide"
}
```

**Available UI Components:** `/Users/jbouder/repos/jbouder/acolyte/components/ui/`
- `badge.tsx` - Badge component
- `button.tsx` - Button with CVA variants (default, destructive, outline, secondary, ghost, link)
- `card.tsx` - Card layout component
- `dialog.tsx` - Modal dialog (built on Radix UI)
- `dropdown-menu.tsx` - Dropdown menu (Radix UI)
- `input.tsx` - Text input field
- **`select.tsx`** - Searchable select component (Radix UI)  IMPORTANT FOR SEARCH
- `separator.tsx` - Visual separator
- `sheet.tsx` - Side sheet/drawer
- `sidebar.tsx` - Full sidebar navigation system
- `skeleton.tsx` - Loading skeleton
- `sonner.tsx` - Toast notifications
- `table.tsx` - Table component
- `tabs.tsx` - Tab navigation
- `textarea.tsx` - Multi-line text input
- `tooltip.tsx` - Tooltip (Radix UI)

**Icon Library:** Lucide React icons

**Radix UI Dependencies:**
