| `package.json` | Modified | Add `cmdk` dependency |
| `lib/tools-data.ts` | New | Centralized tool data with types, descriptions, categories, keywords |
| `components/ui/command.tsx` | New | shadcn Command component wrapping `cmdk` |
| `components/site-search.tsx` | New | SiteSearch component with trigger button and command dialog |
| `app/layout.tsx` | Modified | Import and render `<SiteSearch />` in the header |
| `components/app-sidebar.tsx` | Modified | Remove local items array, import from `lib/tools-data.ts` |

