- `/Users/jbouder/repos/jbouder/acolyte/lib/tools-data.ts` - New file: centralized tool index that is the foundation for both search and sidebar
- `/Users/jbouder/repos/jbouder/acolyte/components/ui/command.tsx` - New file: shadcn Command component wrapping cmdk, required by SiteSearch
- `/Users/jbouder/repos/jbouder/acolyte/components/site-search.tsx` - New file: the main search component with dialog, keyboard shortcut, and navigation
- `/Users/jbouder/repos/jbouder/acolyte/app/layout.tsx` - Existing file: header where SiteSearch is integrated (line 64-69)
- `/Users/jbouder/repos/jbouder/acolyte/components/app-sidebar.tsx` - Existing file: refactor to consume shared tool data instead of local array

